                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17930410-93-off500 t17930410-93-cd501"></join>, a cotton gown, value 15 s. a stuff petticoat, value 5 s. a cloth cloak value<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179304100110"></xptr>18 s. three check aprons, value 5 s. the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17930410-93-victim863" type="victimName">
